{{Quote|I'm killin' those moldspawns because they killed my family, see? Because they disembowelled Garnu Hral Eschen, because they tore the flesh off the bones of the children of Ethras, because they&hellip;|Sergeant Knezex Hral Piksoar|<ref name="Planet of Twilight">''[[Planet of Twilight]]''</ref>}}
'''Ethras''' was a [[Drovian]] whose children had their flesh torn off by members of the [[Gopso'o]] tribe. [[Sergeant/Legends|Sergeant]] [[Knezex Hral Piksoar]] kept Ethras alive in his memories, invoking his name when he attacked Gopso'o.

